xccdf:description.xhtml:p:
Chrome provides a Cleanup feature to detect unwanted software. If this setting is           Enabled
, the results of the cleanup may be shared with Google (based on the setting of           SafeBrowsingExtendedReportingEnabled
) to assist with future unwanted software detection. These results will contain file metadata, automatically installed extensions, and registry keys.

